## Použití TypeScript connectoru

```typescript
import { loadCredentials } from '@cliqsales/connectors/<provider>/auth';
import { getInvoices, getCustomers } from '@cliqsales/connectors/<provider>/operations';

const creds = loadCredentials();
const invoices = await getInvoices(creds, { from: '2026-01-01', to: '2026-12-31' });
```

